snippet.title: Version 5.0 "Flowers Resplendent on the Sun-Scorched Sojourn" Trailer | Genshin Impact #Natlan
snippet.description:
A competition as fierce as a roaring inferno, and a clash as dazzling as a cascade of iridescent gems.
On a hallowed night, the sparks ignited by warriors fall like stars, converging into the triumphant return of the sacred flame.

VA:
"The Captain" Il Capitano — Chris Tergliafera
Chasca — Lauren Amante
Mavuika — Katiana Sarkissian
Kachina — Kristen McGuire
Mualani — Cassandra Lee Morris
Kinich — John Patneaude
Iansan — Katrina Salisbury
Paimon — Corina Boettger
Aether — Zach Aguilar
